hadiths[68]{hadithnumber,text}:
1120,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab raat mein tahajjud ke liye khadey hotey to ye dua padhtey. اللهم لك الحمد أنت قيم السموات والأرض ومن فيهن ولك الحمد ، Mina padhi. لك ملك السموات والأرض ومن فيهن ، Mina padhi. ولك الحمد أنت نور السموات والأرض ، Mina padhi. ولك الحمد أنت الحق ، Mina padhi. ووعدك الحق ، Mina padhi. ولقاؤك حق ، Mina padhi. وقولك حق ، Mina padhi. والجنة حق ، Mina padhi. والنار حق ، Mina padhi. والنبيون حق ، Mina padhi. ومحمد صلى الله عليه وسلم حق ، Mina padhi. والساعة حق ، Mina padhi. اللهم لك أسلمت ، Mina padhi. وبك آمنت وعليك توكلت ، Mina padhi. وإليك أنبت ، Mina padhi. وبك خاصمت ، Mina padhi. وإليك حاكمت ، Mina padhi. فاغفر لي ما قدمت وما أخرت ، Mina padhi. وما أسررت وما أعلنت ، Mina padhi. أنت المقدم وأنت المؤخر ، Mina ‏‏‏‏لا إله إلا أنت ، لا إله غيرك(tarjama) ''aey mere Allaah! har tarah ki tareef terey hi liye zebaa hai, to aasman aur zameen aur unmein rehney wali tamam makhlooq ka sanbhaalney wala hai aur hamd tamam ki tamam bas terey hi liye munasib hai aasman aur zameen aur unki tamam makhlooqat par hukumat sirf terey hi liye hai aur tareef terey hi liye hai, to aasman aur zameen ka noor hai aur tareef terey hi liye zebaa hai, to sachcha hai, tera wada sachchaa, teri mulaqat sachchii, tera farman sachcha hai, jannat sach hai, dozakh sach hai, anbiya sachey hain. Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sachey hain aur qiyamat ka hona sach hai. aey mere Allaah! main tera hi farmaanbardaar hun aur tujhii par eman rakhta hun, tujhii par bharosa hai, teri hi taraf rujoo karta hun, terey hi ata kiye huey dalaayel ke zariey bahas karta hun aur tujhii ko hakam (faisla karnewaalaa) banata hun. to jo khataein mujh se pahley huin aur jo baad mein hongi un sab ki maghfirat farma, chahe wo zahir hui hon ya posheeda. aagey karne wala aur peechhey rakhney wala to hi hai. maabood sirf to hi hai. ya (ye kaha ke) terey siwa koi maabood nahin''. Abu-Sufiyan ne bayan kya ke Abdul-Karim abu-umaiya ne us dua mein ye zyadti ki hai لا حول wla قوة إلا بالله Sufiyaan ne bayan kya ke Sulaimaan-bin-Muslim ne Taaus se ye hadis suni thi, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se."
1121,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zindagi mein jab koi khuwab dekhta to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan karta (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tabeer detey) mere bhi dil mein ye khahish paida hui ke main bhi koi khuwab dekhta aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan karta, main abhi naujawaan tha aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein masjid mein sota tha. chunanche maine khuwab mein dekha ke 2 Farishtey mujhey pakad kar dozakh ki taraf ley gaey. maine dekha ke dozakh par kuwein ki tarah bandish hai (yani is par kuwein ki si munder bani hui hai) iske 2 rastey they. dozakh mein bahut se aisey logon ko dekha jinhein main pehchanta tha. main kehney laga dozakh se Allah ki panaah! unhon-ne bayan kya ke phir ham ko aik farishta mila aur us ne mujh se kaha daro nahi."
1122,ye khuwab maine (apni behan ( Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ko sunaya aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko . tabeer mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Abdullah bahut khub ladka hai. kash! raat mein Namaz padha karta. ( rawi ne kaha ke aap ke us farman ke baad) Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) raat mein bahut kam sotey they ( zyada ibadat hi kartey rahtey ( .
1123,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (raat mein) gyara (11) rakatein padhtey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki yahi Namaz thi. lekin iske sajdey itney lambey hua kartey ke tum mein se koi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sar uthaney se qabl pachaas aayatein padh sakta tha (aur tuloo fajr honey par) fajr ki Namaz se pahley Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) 2 rakaat sunnat padhtey. iske baad daain pahlu par let jatey. aakhir muazzan Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Namaz ke liye bulaney aataa.
1124,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bimar huey to aik ya 2 raat tak (namaz ke liye) na uth sakey.
1125,Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) (eik martaba kuchh dinon tak) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas (wahiy lekar ( nahi aaey to Quraish ki aik aurat (umme-Jameel abu-Lahab ki beewii) ne kaha ke ab iske shaitan ne iske paas aaney se der lagaaii. is par ye sura utrii ( والضحى * والليل إذا سجى * ما ودعك ربك وما قلى‏ ( .
1126,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik raat jaagey to farmaya Subhan-Allah ! aaj raat kya kya balaaein utri hain aur sath hi ( rehmat aur inayat ke) kaisey khazaaney nazil huey hain. un hujrey waaliyon (paak beeviyon) ko koi jagaanewaalaa wala hai, afsos! ke duniya mein bahut si kapdey pahnney wali auratein aakhirat mein nangii hongii."
1127,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik raat unke aur Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ke paas aaey, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kya tum log (tahajjud ki) Namaz nahi padhogey? maine kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! hamari roohein Allah ke qabze mein hain, jab wo chaahega hamein utha dega. hamari us arz par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wapas tashrif ley gaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne koi jawab nahi diya lekin wapas jatey huey maine suna ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raan par hath mar kar) sura Kahaf ki ye aayat padh rahe they) aadmi sabse zyada jhagdaaloo hai) وكان الإنسان أكثر شىء جدلا‏ ( ."
1128,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik kaam ko chhod detey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko iska karna pasand hota. us khayal se tark kar detey ke doosrey sahaba bhi is par (aapko dekh kar) amal shuru kar dein aur is tarah wo kaam un par farz ho jaey. chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chasht ki Namaz kabhi nahi padhi lekin main padhti hun.
1129,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik raat masjid mein Namaz padhi. sahaba ne bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ye Namaz padhi. dusri raat bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye Namaz padhi to namaziyon ki tadaad bahut badh gaee teesri ya chothi raat to pura ijtimaa hi ho gaya tha. lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us raat Namaz padhaaney tashrif nahi laey. subah ke waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum log jitni badi tadaad mein jama ho gaey they. maine usey dekha lekin mujhey bahar aaney se ye khayal rukawat raha ke kahin tum par ye Namaz farz na ho jaey. ye Ramazan ka waqia tha.
1130,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) itni der tak khadey ho kar Namaz padhtey rahtey ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qadam ya (ye kaha ke) pindliyon par waram aa jata, jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iske mutaalliq kuchh arz kya jata to farmatey ''kya main Allah ka shukr-guzar banda na banoon''."
1131,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke sab namazon mein Allah Taala ke nazdeek pasandida Namaz Dawud (Alaihissalam) ki Namaz hai aur rozon mein bhi Dawud (Alaihissalam) hi ka roza. aap aadhi raat tak sotey, iske baad tehai raat Namaz padhney mein guzaartey. phir raat ke chhatey hissey mein bhi so jatey. isi tarah aap aik din roza rakhtey aur aik din iftaar kartey they."
1132,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko kon sa amal zyada pasand tha? aap ne jawab diya ke jis par hameshgii ki jaey (chaahe wo koi bhi nek kaam ho ( maine malum kya ke aap (raat mein Namaz ke liye) Kab khadey hotey they? aap ne farmaya ke jab murgh ki awaz suntey. ham se Muhammad-bin salam ne bayan kya, kaha ke hamein abul-Ahwas Salaam-binSaleem ne khabar di, unse Ashas ne bayan kya ke murgh ki awaz suntey hi aap khadey ho jatey aur Namaz padhtey."
1133,Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) ne batlaya ke unhon-ne apne yahan subah (sehar) ke waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko hamesha letey huey paya.
1134,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Zaid-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) donon ne mil kar sehrii khaai, sehrii se farigh ho kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz ke liye khadey ho gaey aur donon ne Namaz padhi. ham ne Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke sehrii se faraghat aur Namaz shuru karne ke darmyan kitna fasla raha hoga? aap ne jawab diya ke itni der mein aik aadmi pachaas aayatein padh sakta hai."
1135,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik martaba raat ko Namaz padhi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne itna lamba qiyam kya ke mere dil mein aik ghalat khayal paida ho gaya. ham ne puchha ke wo ghalat khayal kya tha to aap ne bataya ke maine sochaa ke baith jaun aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka sath chhod dun.
1136,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab raat ko tahajjud ke liye khadey hotey to pahley apna munh miswak se khub saaf kartey.
1137,Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya aik shakhs ne malum kya ya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! raat ki Namaz kis tarah padhi jaaey? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya 2-2 rakaat aur jab subah honey ka andesha ho to aik rakaat witr padh kar apni saari Namaz ko taaq bana ley.
1138,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki raat ki Namaz 13 rakaat hoti thi.
1139,"maine Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki raat ki Namaz ke mutaalliq puchha to aap ne farmaya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) saat (7) , nau (9) aur gyara (11) tak rakatein padhtey they. fajr ki sunnat iske siwa hoti."
1140,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat ko 13 rakatein padhtey they. witr aur fajr ki 2 sunnat rakatein usi mein hotiin.
1141,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kisi maheene mein roza na rakhtey to aisa malum hota ke ab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us maheene mein roza hi nahi rakhengey aur agar kisi maheene mein roza rakhna shuru kartey to khayal hota ke ab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka us maheene ka aik din bhi baghair roze ke nahi reh jaeyga aur raat ko Namaz to aisi padhtey they ke tum jab chahtey aapko Namaz padhtey dekh letey aur jab chahtey sota dekh letey Muhammad-bin-Jafar ke sath us hadis ko Sulaiman aur abu-Khalid ne bhi Humaid se riwayat kya hai.
1142,rasool akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke shaitan aadmi ke sar ke peechhey raat mein sotey waqt teen girhein laga deta hai aur har gireh par ye mantr phoonk deta hai ke so ja abhi raat bahut baqi hai phir agar koi bedaar hokar Allah ki yad karne laga to aik girah khul jati hai phir jab wuzu karta hai to dusri girah khul jati hai. phir agar Namaz (farz ya nafl) padhey to teesri girah bhi khul jati hai. is tarah subah ke waqt aadmi chaaq w chauband khush mizaaj rehta hai. warna sust aur bd-baatin rehta hai.
1143,unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khuwab bayan kartey huey farmaya ke jiska sar patthar se kuchlaa ja raha tha wo Quran ka Hafiz tha magar wo Quran se ghaafil ho gaya aur farz Namaz padhey baghair so jaya karta tha.
1144,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney aik shakhs ka zikr aaya ke wo subah tak padaa sota raha aur farz Namaz ke liye bhi nahi uthaa. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke shaitan ne uske kaan mein peshab kar diya hai.
1145,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke hamara parwardigar buland barkat wala hai har raat ko us waqt aasmaane-duniyaa par aata hai jab raat ka aakhiri tehai hissey reh jata hai. wo kehta hai koi mujh se dua karne wala hai ke main uski dua qabool karun koi mujh se maangney wala hai ke main usey dun, koi mujh se bakhshish talab karne wala hai ke main usko bakhsh dun."
1146,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat mein Namaz kaise padhtey they? aap ne batlaya ke shuru raat mein so rahtey aur aakhir raat mein bedaar ho kar tahajjud ki Namaz padhtey. iske baad bistar par aa jatey aur jab muazzan azan deta to jaldi se uth baithtey. agar ghusl ki zarurat hoti to ghusl kartey warna wuzu karke bahar tashrif ley jatey.
1147,Ummul-Momenin Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) se unhon-ne puchha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Ramazan main (raat ko) kitni rakatein padhtey they. aap ne jawab diya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (raat mein) gyara (11) rakaton se zyada nahi padhtey they. chahe Ramazan ka mahina hota ya koi aur . pahley Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) char rakaat padhtey . unki khoobi aur lambai ka kya poochhna . phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) char rakaat aur padhtey unki khoobi aur lambai ka kya poochhna . phir teen rakatein padhtey . Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya ke maine arz kya ya Rasulullah! aap witr padhney se pahley hi so jatey hain? is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Aaisha! meri aankhen soti hain lekin mera dil nahi sota.
1148,Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) ne batlaya ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko raat ki kisi Namaz mein baith kar Quran padhtey nahi dekha. yahan tak ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) boodhey ho gaey to baith kar Quran padhtey they lekin jab tees chalis (40) aayatein reh jaatiin to khadey ho jatey phir usko padh kar rukoo kartey they.
1149,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) se fajr ke waqt puchha ke aey Bilal ! mujhey apna sabse zyada ummeed wala nek kaam bataao jisey tum ne Islam laney ke baad kya hai, kyonke maine jannat main apne aagey tumharey jooton ki chaap suni hai. Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya maine to apne nazdeek us se zyada ummeed ka koi kaam nahi kya ke jab maine raat ya din mein kisi waqt bhi wuzu kya to main us wuzu se nafl Namaz padhta rehta jitni meri taqdeer likhi gaee thi."
1150,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjid mein tashrif ley gaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki nazar aik rassii par padi jo 2 sutunon ke darmyan tanii hui thi. malum farmaya ke ye rassii kaisi hai? logon ne kaha ke ye Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ne baandhii hai jab wo (namaz mein khadii-khadii) thak jati hain to us se latkii rehti hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi ye rassii nahi honii chahiye usey khol daalo, tum mein har shakhs ko chahiye jab tak dil lagey Namaz padhey, thak jaey to baith jaey."
1151,"mere paas banu-Asad ki aik aurat baithi thi, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey to unke mutaalliq puchha ke ye kon hain? maine kaha ke ye falan khatun hain jo raat bhar nahi sotiin. unki Namaz ka Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney zikr kya gaya. lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke bas tumhen sirf itna hi amal karna chahiye jitney ki tum mein taqat ho. kyonke Allah Taala to (sawab dene se) thaktaa hi nahi tum hi amal kartey kartey thak jaogey."
1152,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aey Abdullaah! falan ki tarah na ho jana wo raat mein ibadat kya karta tha phir chhod di aur Hisham bin Ammar ne kaha ke ham se abdul-Hameed-bin-Abu-Ishreen ne bayan kya, unse imam Auzai ne bayan kya, kaha ke mujh se Yahya ne bayan kya, unse Amr-bin-Hakam-bin-Sobaan ne bayan kya, kaha ke mujh se abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne, isi tarah phir yahi hadis bayan ki, ibne-abii-Ishreen ki tarah Amr-bin-Abii Salma ne bhi usko imam Auzai se riwayat kya."
1153,"mujh se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha ke kya ye khabar sahi hai ke tum raat bhar ibadat kartey ho aur phir din mein rozey rakhtey ho? maine kaha ke ji haan, ya Rasulullah! main aisa hi karta hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke lekin agar tum aisa karogey to tumhari aankhen (bedaarii ki wjah se) baith jaeyngi aur teri jaan kamzor ho jaeygi. ye jaan lo ke tum par tumharey nafs ka bhi haq hai aur biwi bachchon ka bhii. isliye kabhi roza bhi rakho aur kabhi bila rozey ke bhi raho, ibadat bhi karo aur so'o bhii."
1154,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jo shakhs raat ko bedaar ho kar ye dua padhey لا إله إلا الله وحده لا شريك له ، Mina له الملك ، Mina وله الحمد ، Mina وهو على كل شىء قدير‏ . Mina الحمد لله ، Mina وسبحان الله ، Mina wla إله إلا الله ، Mina والله أكبر ، Mina wla حول wla قوة إلا بالله ( tarjama ( ''Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi wo akelaa hai uska koi Sharik nahi mulk usi ke liye hai aur tamam ta'reefein bhi usi ke liye hain, aur wo har cheez par qaadir hai. tamam ta'reefein Allah hi ke liye hain, Allah ki zaat paak hai, Allah Taala ke siwa koi maabood nahi aur Allah sabse bada hai, Allah ki madad ke baghair na kisi ko gunahon se bchney ki taqat hai na neki karne ki himmat'' phir ye padhey ( اللهم اغفر لي‏ ( ) tarjama (aey Allaah! meri maghfirat farmaa''. ya (ye kaha ke) koi dua karey to uski dua qabool hoti hai. phir agar usne wuzu kya (aur Namaz padhi ( to Namaz bhi maqbool hoti hai."
1155,"tumharey bhai ne (apne naa'tiya ashaar mein) ye koi ghalat baat nahi kahi. aap ki murad Abdullaah-bin-Rawaaha (Raziallahu anhu) aur unke ashaar se thi jinka tarjama ye hai : ''ham mein Allah ke rasool maujood hain, jo uski kitab us waqt hamein sunatey hain jab fajr tuloo' hoti hai. ham to andhey they Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein gumrahi se nikal kar sahi rasta dikhaayaa. unki baatein usi qadr yaqeeni hain jo hamarey dilon ke andar ja kar baith jati hain aur jo kuchh aap ne farmaya wo zaroor hokar rahega. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat bistar se apne ko alag karke guzaartey hain jabke mushrikon se unke bistar bojhal ho rahe hotey hain''. Yunus ki tarah us hadis ko Aqeel ne bhi Zohri se riwayat kya aur Zubaidi ne yun kaha Saeed-bin-Musaiyab aur Aaraj se, unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se."
1156,maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein ye khuwab dekha ke maano aik gaadhey reshamii kapdey ka aik tukda mere hath hai. jaisey mein jannat mein jis jagah ka bhi irada karta hun to ye idhar uda ke mujh ko ley jata hai aur maine dekha ke jaisey-jaisey Farishtey mere paas aaey aur unhon-ne mujhey dozakh ki taraf ley janey ka irada kya hi tha ke aik farishta unse aa kar mila aur (mujh se) kaha ke daro nahi (aur unse kaha ke) usey chhod do.
1157,to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Abdullah bada hi achchha aadmi hai kash! raat ko bhi Namaz padha karta. Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) iske baad hamesha raat ko Namaz padha kartey they.
1158,bahut se sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se apne khuwab bayan kiye ke shabe-qadr (ramazaan ki) sattaiswin raat hai. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main dekh raha hun ke tum sab ke khuwab Ramazan ke aakhiri ashrey mein (shabe-qadr ke honey par) muttafiq ho gaey hain. isliye jisey shabe-qadr ki talash ho wo Ramazan ke aakhiri ashrey mein dhoondey.
1159,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne isha ki Namaz padhi phir raat ko uth kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tahajjud ki aath (8) rakatein padhein aur 2 rakatein subah ki azan w iqamat ke darmyan padhein jinko Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kabhi nahi chhodtey they (fajr ki sunnaton par hamesha qaayem rahe) .
1160,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) fajr ki 2 sunnat rakatein padhney ke baad daain karwat par let jatey.
1161,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab fajr ki sunnatein padh chuktey to agar main jaagtii hoti to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mujh se baatein kartey warna let jatey jab tak Namaz ki azan hoti .
1162,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamein apne tamam maamlaat mein istikhaara karne ki isi tarah taleem detey they jis tarah Quran ki koi sura sikhlaatey . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey ke jab koi aham mamla tumharey samney ho to farz ke ilawa 2 rakaat nafl padhney ke baad ye dua padhey اللهم إني أستخيرك بعلمك وأستقدرك بقدرتك ، Mina وأسألك من فضلك العظيم ، Mina فإنك تقدر wla أقدر وتعلم wla أعلم وأنت علام الغيوب ، Mina اللهم إن كنت تعلم أن هذا الأمر خير لي في ديني ومعاشي وعاقبة أمري ( أو قال ( ) عاجل أمري وآجله فاقدره لي ويسره لي ثم بارك لي فيه ، وإن كنت تعلم أن هذا الأمر شر لي في ديني ومعاشي وعاقبة أمري أو قال في عاجل أمري وآجله فاصرفه عني واصرفني عنه ، Mina واقدر لي الخير( tarjama ( ''aey mere Allah ! main tujh se terey ilm ki badaulat khair talab karta hun aur teri qudrat ki badaulat tujh se taqat mangta hun aur terey fazale-azeem ka talabgaar hun ke qudrat to hi rakhta hai aur mujhey koi qudrat nahi. ilm tujh hi ko hai aur main kuchh nahi janta aur to tamam chhipii baton ko jaanney wala hai. aey mere Allaah! agar to janta hai ke ye kaam jiske liye istikhaara kya ja raha hai mere deen-duniyaa aur mere kaam ke anjam ke eitibaar se mere liye behtar hai ya (aap ne ye farmaya ke) mere liye waqti taur par aur anjam ke eitibaar se ye (khair hai) to usey mere liye naseeb kar aur iska hasil karna mere liye aasan kar aur phir usmein mujhey barkat ata kar aur agar to janta hai ke ye kaam mere deen, duniya aur mere kaam ke anjam ke eitibaar se bura hai. ya (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye kaha ke) mere maamle mein waqti taur par aur anjam ke eitibaar se (buraa hai) to usey mujh se hata de aur mujhey bhi us se hata de. phir mere liye khair muqaddar farma de, jahan bhi wo ho aur us se mere dil ko mut'ma'in bhi kar de''. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us kaam ki jagah us kaam ka naam ley."
1163,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jab koi tum mein se masjid mein aaey to na baithey jab tak 2 rakaat ( تحیۃ المسجد ki) na padh ley.
1164,hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( hamarey ghar mein jab dawat mein aaey they) 2 rakaat Namaz padhai aur phir wapas tashrif ley gaey.
1165,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Zohar se pahley 2 rakaat sunnat padhi aur Zohar ke baad 2 rakaat aur Juma ke baad 2 rakaat aur maghrib ke baad 2 rakaat aur isha ke baad bhi 2 rakaat (namaz sunnat) padhi hai.
1166,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Juma ka khutba detey huey farmaya ke jo shakhs bhi (masjid mein) aaey aur imam khutba de raha ho ya khutbe ke liye nikal chuka ho to wo 2 rakaat Namaz ( تحیۃ المسجد ki) padh ley.
1167,"Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) (Makka sharif mein) apne ghar aaey. kisi ne kaha baithey kya ho Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ye aagey balke Kaba ke andar bhi tashrif ley ja chukey hain. Abdullah ne kaha ye sun kar mein aaya. dekha to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Kaba se bahar nikal chukey hain aur Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) darwazey par khadey hain. maine unse puchha ke aey Bilal ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Kaba mein Namaz padhi ? unhon-ne kaha ke haan, padhi thi. maine puchha ke kahan padhi thi? unhon-ne bataya ke yahan un 2 sutunon ke darmyan . phir aap bahar tashrif laey aur 2 rakatein Kaba ke darwazey ke samney padhein aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke mujhey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chasht ki 2 rakaton ki wasiiyat ki thi aur Utban ne farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) subah din chadhey mere ghar tashrif laey. ham ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey saf bana li aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 2 rakaat Namaz padhai."
1168,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab 2 rakaat (fajr ki sunnat) padh chuktey to us waqt agar main jaagtii hoti to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mujh se baatein kartey warna let jatey. maine Sufiyan se kaha ke kuchh rawi fajr ki 2 rakatein usey bataatey hain to unhon-ne farmaya ke haan, ye wahi hain."
1169,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kisi nafl Namaz ki fajr ki 2 rakaton se zyada pabandi nahi kartey they.
1170,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat mein 13 rakatein padhtey they. phir jab subah ki azan suntey to 2 halki rakatein (sunnat fajr) padh letey.
1171,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (doosri sanad) aur ham se Ahmad-bin-Yoonus ne bayan kya, kaha ke ham se Zuhair ne bayan kya, kaha ke ham se Yahya-bin-Saeed Ansari ne bayan kya, unse Muhammad-bin Abdur-Rehman ne, unse Umra-bint-Abdur-Rehmaan ne aur unse Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) ne ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) subah ki) farz ( Namaz se pahley ki 2 (sunnat) rakaton ko bahut mukhtasar rakhtey they. aap ne unmein sura Fatiha bhi padhi ya nahi mein ye bhi nahi keh sakti ."
1172,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Zohar se pahley 2 rakaat sunnat, Zohar ke baad 2 rakaat sunnat, maghrib ke baad 2 rakaat sunnat, isha ke baad 2 rakaat sunnat aur Juma ke baad 2 rakaat sunnat padhi hain aur maghrib aur isha ki sunnatein aap ghar mein padhtey they. abu-Zinaad ne Musa-bin-Aqba ke waaste se bayan kya aur unse Naafe ne ke isha ke baad apne ghar mein (sunnat padhtey they) unki riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Kaseer-bin-Farqad aur Ayub ne Naafe ke waaste se ki hai."
1173,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) fajr honey ke baad 2 halki rakatein ( sunnate-fajr ( padhtey aur ye aisa waqt hota ke main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas nahi jati thi. Ubaidullah ke sath us hadis ko kaseer-bin-Farqad aur Ayub ne bhi Naafe se riwayat kya aur ibne- abii-Zinaad ne us hadis ko Musa-bin-Aqba se, unhon-ne Naafe se riwayat kya. usmein ( في بيته (ke badal ( في أهله‏ ( hai."
1174,maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aath (8) rakaat aik sath (zuhar aur Asr (aur saat (7) rakaat aik sath ( maghrib aur isha mila kar) padhein. ( beech mein sunnat wghaira kuchh nahi ( Abul-Sha'a-Sa'a se maine kaha mera khayal hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zohar aakhir waqt main aur Asr awwal waqt mein padhi hogi. isi tarah maghrib aakhir waqt mein padhi hogi aur isha awwal waqt mein. Abul-Sha'a-Sa'a ne kaha ke mera bhi yahi khayal hai.
1175,kya aap chasht ki Namaz padhtey hain? unhon-ne farmaya ke nahi. maine puchha aur umr padhtey they? aap ne farmaya ke nahi. maine puchha aur Abu-Bakar (rz)? farmaya nahi. maine puchha aur Nabi Karim (sl)? farmaya nahi. mera khayal yahi hai.
1176,"mujh se Umme-Hani (Raziallahu anhu) ke siwa kisi (sahaabii) ne ye nahi bayan kya ke unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko chasht ki Namaz padhtey dekha hai. sirf Umme-Hani (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke fateh Makka ke din Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke ghar tashrif laaey, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ghusl kya aur phir aath (8) rakaat (chaasht ki) Namaz padhi. to maine aisi halki phulkii Namaz kabhi nahi dekhi. albatta Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rukoo aur sajda poori tarah ada kartey they."
1177,maine to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko chasht ki Namaz padhtey nahi dekha magar main khud padhti hun.
1178,mujhey mere jaani dost (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) ne teen chizon ki wasiiyat ki hai ke maut se pahley unko na chhodun . har maheene mein teen din rozey. chasht ki Namaz aur witr padh kar sonaa.
1179,"Ansar mein se aik shakhs (Utbaan bin Maalik) ne jo bahut motey aadmi they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz kya ke main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhney ki taqat nahi rakhta (mujh ko ghar par Namaz padhney ki ijazat dijiye to) unhon-ne apne ghar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye khana pakwaayaa aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko apne ghar bulaya aur aik chatai ke kinarey ko Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye pani se saaf kya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par 2 rakaat Namaz padhi aur fulaan-bin-fulaan-bin-Jaarood ne Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke kya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chasht ki Namaz padha kartey they? to aap ne farmaya ke maine us roz ke siwa Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko kabhi ye Namaz padhtey nahi dekha."
1180,"mujhey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se das rakaat sunnatein yad hain. 2 rakaat sunnat Zohar se pahley, 2 rakaat sunnat Zohar ke ba'd, 2 rakaat sunnat maghrib ke baad apne ghar mein, 2 rakaat sunnat isha ke baad apne ghar main aur 2 rakaat sunnat subah ki Namaz se pahley aur ye wo waqt hota tha jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas koi nahi jata tha."
1181,muazzan jab azan deta aur fajr ho jati to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) 2 rakatein padhtey.
1182,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Zohar se pahley char rakaat sunnat aur subah ki Namaz se pahley 2 rakaat sunnat Namaz padhni nahi chhodtey they. Yahya ke sath us hadis ko ibne-abii-Adii aur Amr-bin-Marzooq ne bhi Shoba se riwayat kya.
1183,unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne irshad farmaya ke maghrib ke farz se pahley (sunnat ki 2 rakatein) padha karo. teesri martaba Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yun farmaya ke jiska ji chahey kyonke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye baat pasand na thi ke log usey lazimi samajh baithein.
1184,mein Aqba-bin-Aamir Johni sahabi (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya aur arz kya aapko abu-Tameem Abdullah-bin Malik par tajjub nahi aaya ke wo maghrib ki Namaz farz se pahley 2 rakaat nafl padhtey hain. is par Aqba ne farmaya ke ham bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein usey padhtey they. maine kaha phir ab iske chhodney ki kya wjah hai? unhon-ne farmaya ke duniya ke karobar rukawat hain.
1185,unhein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) yad hain aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wo kulli bhi yad hai jo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke ghar ke kuwein se pani lekar unke munh mein ki thi.
1186,"jo badr ki ladai main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Sharik they, wo kehtey they ke main apni qaum banii-Saalim ko Namaz padhaayaa karta tha mere ( ghar (aur qaum ki masjid ke beech mein aik naala tha, aur jab barish hoti to usey paar karke masjid tak pahunchnaa mere liye mushkil ho jata tha. chunanche main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se maine kaha ke meri aankhen kharaab ho gaee hain aur aik naala hai jo mere aur meri qaum ke darmyan padta hai, wo barish ke dinon mein bahney lag jata hai aur mere liye iska paar karna mushkil ho jata hai. meri ye khahish hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif la kar mere ghar kisi jagah Namaz padh dein taake main usey apne liye Namaz padhney ki jagah muqarrar kar loon. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main tumhari ye khahish jald hi poori karunga. phir doosrey hi din Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko sath lekar subah tashrif ley aaey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ijazat chahi aur maine ijazat de di. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif la kar baithey bhi nahi balke puchha ke tum apne ghar mein kis jagah mere liye Namaz padhna pasand karogey. mein jis jagah ko Namaz padhney ke liye pasand kar chuka tha uski taraf maine ishara kar diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wahan khadey ho kar takbeere-tahreema kahi aur ham sab ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey saf baandh li. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein 2 rakaat Namaz padhai phir salam pheraa. ham ne bhi aap ke sath salam pheraa. maine haleem khaney ke liye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko rok liya jo taiyaar ho raha tha. mohalle walon ne jo suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere ghar tashrif farma hain to log jaldi jaldii jama honey shuru ho gaey aur ghar mein aik khaasaa majma' ho gaya. unmein se aik shakhs bola. Malik ko kya ho gaya hai ! yahan dikhai nahi detaa. is par doosra bola wo to munafiq hai. usey Allah aur rasool se mohabbat nahi hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya, aisa mat kaho, dekhtey nahi ke wo ( لا إله إلا الله ( padhta hai aur us se uska maqsad Allah Taala ki khushnoodii hai. tab wo kehney laga ke (asl haal) to Allah aur rasool ko malum hai. lekin Allah ki qasam! ham to unki baat cheet aur mel-jol zahir mein munaafiqon hi se dekhtey hain. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya lekin Allah Taala ne har us aadmi par dozakh haram kar di hai jisne ( لا إله إلا الله ( Allah ki raza aur khushnoodii ke liye keh liyaa. Mehmood-bin Rabe ne bayan kya ke maine ye hadis aik aisi jagah mein bayan ki jis main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke mashhoor sahabi Abu-Ayub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) bhi maujood they. ye Rome (mojooda Itly) ke us jihad ka zikr hai jis mein aap ki maut ho gaee thi. fauj ke sardaar Yazeed-bin-Muaawiya they. Abu-Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) ne us hadis se inkar kya aur farmaya ke Allah ki qism ! main nahi samajhta ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aisi baat kabhi bhi kahi ho. aap ki ye guftgu mujh ko bahut na-gawar guzri aur maine Allah Taala ki mannat maana ke agar main us jihad se salamati ke sath lota to waapsii par us hadis ke barey mein Utbaan-bin-Maalik (Raziallahu anhu) se zaroor poochhoonga. agar maine unhein unki qaum ki masjid mein zinda paya. aakhir mein jihad se wapas hua. pahley to maine Haj aur Umre ka ehram baandha phir jab Madina waapsii hui to main qabila bano Salim mein aaya. Utban (Raziallahu anhu) jo boodhey aur naa-beenaa ho gaey they, apni qaum ko Namaz padhatey huey miley. salam pherney ke baad maine hazir ho kar aapko salam kya aur batlaya ke main falan hun. phir maine us hadis ke mutaalliq malum kya to aap ne mujh se us martaba bhi is tarah ye hadis bayan ki jis tarah pahley bayan ki thi."
1187,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke apne gharon mein bhi kuchh namazein padha karo aur unhein bilkul qabrein na bana lo (ke jahan Namaz hi na padhi jati ho) Wuhaib ke sath us hadis ko abdul-wahaab Saqafi ne bhi Ayub se riwayat kya hai.
